Name: Saint Hill
AboutMe:
Wizard of the Oz programming language. That's my big project and when it materializes, all other programming domains will crumble before the all-powerful, syntactically beautiful and functionally implicit Oz!

I dabble in Java, Groovy, Fortran, Scala, DOS and just about anything else required to get the job done in a multidisciplinary, undisciplined and uncouth-although-amazing software environment.

All life's problems can be solved with concision and contrition. Be concise and never forget to have fun and learn a bit too.

Never take yourself or anyone else too seriously -- that only leads to bugzz.

Cheers y'all!
